Heavy metal in the Arctic? Not the music; chemicals like arsenic & mercury in the soil. @ClaricePerryman et al analyzed 1000+ samples via data in the @USGS Alaskan Geochemical Database to map #HeavyMetal concentrations in #Alaska. Read more: https://t.co/EPcaCqcsjX #TechTuesday https://t.co/O07Q1WiM2H
